{
  "page": "Battle under the walls of Riverrun",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle under the walls of Riverrun</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/32px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/48px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/64px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/32px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/48px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/64px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/32px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/48px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/64px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\"><img alt=\"House Piper.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/20px-House_Piper.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/30px-House_Piper.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/40px-House_Piper.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">House Piper</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/20px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/30px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/40px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Tytos Blackwood</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">~15,000<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      force scattered<br />many knights captured<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> (captured)</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>battle under the walls of Riverrun</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is the second major battle of the conflict known as the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Battle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> defeats the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">Pipers</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">Vances</a> in a <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth\">battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Piper\" title=\"Clement Piper\">Clement Piper</a> falls back to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Jaime and  his father, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, invade the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> with separate hosts. Jaime marches directly on Riverrun, where Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> has assembled many of his father <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a>'s bannermen and knights. Edmure's force is diminished on account of the men he has sent to guard the borders and the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a> in response to Lannister raiding. The forces of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> are also not present.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jaime meets the Tullys under the walls of Riverrun. Securing a victory, Jaime puts the <a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">rivermen</a> to rout. Edmure and many of his knights and bannermen are taken captive. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Tytos Blackwood</a> manages to lead some of the surviving men back within Riverrun, where Jaime places them under siege.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tywin leads a second, larger Lannister army against the companies of men Edmure had dispersed along his borders to guard against Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a>'s raiding. Tywin and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a> are able to destroy them piecemeal before they can regroup. They then attack several castles of the river lords, including <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Fall of Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Pinkmaiden_Castle\" title=\"Burning of Pinkmaiden Castle\">Pinkmaiden Castle</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Burning of Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Darry\" title=\"Capture of Darry\">Darry</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Yielding_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Yielding of Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">westermen</a> assume a position at the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruby_ford\" title=\"Ruby ford\">ruby ford</a>, where they can both block any <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">Arryn</a> attempt to relieve Riverrun and can maintain contact with <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Your brother has been covering himself with glory. He smashed the Lords <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Vance</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Piper\" title=\"Clement Piper\">Piper</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>, and met the massed power of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">Tullys</a> under the walls of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>. The lords of the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a> have been put to rout. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> was taken captive, with many of his knights and bannermen. <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Lord Blackwood</a> led a few survivors back to Riverrun, where <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a> has them under siege. The rest fled to their own strongholds.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Is it my fault that <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">your fool brother</a> lost his battle before <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">we</a> could march? I am told the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingslayer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingslayer\">Kingslayer</a> went through him like an axe through ripe cheese.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">Catelyn Tully</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">After the battle, Jaime besieges Riverrun with 12,000 foot and 2,000 or 3,000 horse.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>, Catelyn X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">2.